    75	- `.claude/CLAUDE.md` invocation notes (persona section only; shared body requires meeting)
    76	- `harness/*.py` (orchestration infrastructure)
    77	
    78	### Shared — meeting-gated
    79	
    80	- `operator/OPERATOR.md`, `operator/REGULATION.md`, `operator/STAGE_CONTRACT.md`, `operator/MEETING_PROTOCOL.md`, `operator/PROCESS_AUDIT_CHECKLIST.md`
    81	- `operator/FILE_INDEX.md` (any addition must reference the file's existence)
